# Critical Rules

## Component Separation
- **ONE COMPONENT PER FILE** - no exceptions, even for tiny components
- **NO INLINE JSX** - extract `{items.map(item => <div>...</div>)}` to separate component files
- Related components go in same directory with lowercase-with-dashes naming

## Side Effects
- **NO useEffect/useLayoutEffect in UI components** - components are PRESENTATION ONLY
- Side effects belong in: custom hooks (`hooks/`), providers (`providers/`), or page components
- Before adding side effects: search codebase for similar patterns, then discuss

