# Quick Reference

## Do
- ✅ One component per file
- ✅ React Query for ALL API calls
- ✅ Zustand via `useAppStore` for global state
- ✅ Side effects in custom hooks
- ✅ Named exports
- ✅ `interface` over `type` for objects
- ✅ `function` keyword for components
- ✅ Shadcn UI + Tailwind CSS
- ✅ `cn()` for conditional classes

## Don't
- ❌ Multiple components in one file
- ❌ useEffect in UI components
- ❌ Direct fetch/axios calls in components
- ❌ Enums (use const objects/unions)
- ❌ Default exports
- ❌ Prop drilling (use Zustand/context)
- ❌ Components > 200 lines
